"list\">\n      <h3><a href=\"../../xwdt/xydt.htm\">学院动态</a></h3>\n      <h3><a href=\"../../xwdt/gg.htm\">公告</a></h3>\n      <h3><a href=\"../../xwdt/mtjj.htm\">媒体聚焦</a></h3>\n    </div>\n  </li>\n  <li><h2 class=\"h2\"><a href=\"../../joinus.htm\">加入我们</a></h2>\n    <div class=\"list\">\n      <h3><a href=\"../../joinus/zhaopin.htm\">招聘信息</a></h3>\n    </div>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<!-- 移动端头部e -->\n\n<!-- ny_banner -->\n<div class=\"ny_banner\">\n  <img src=\"../../ny_images/ny_teamxq_banner.jpg\">\n  <div class=\"txt sjcTop\">\n    \n\n\n\n<h5>师资队伍</h5>\n    <span>\n                        <a href=\"../../index.htm\" style=\"    color: #ffffff;\">首页</a>\n                &gt;\n                <a href=\"../../szdw/zzjs.htm\" style=\"    color: #ffffff;\">师资队伍</a>\n                &gt;\n                <a href=\"../../szdw/zzjs.htm\" style=\"    color: #ffffff;\">在职教师</a>\n                &gt;\n                正文\n</span>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- trait -->\n<div class=\"trait\">\n  <div class=\"trait_nr\">\n    <a href=\"../../szdw/zzjs.htm\" title=\"在职教师\" class=\"on\">在职教师</a>\n    <a href=\"../../szdw/jzjs.htm\" title=\"兼职教授\">兼职教授</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- team_nr -->\n<div class=\"team_xq_bg\">\n   \n\n\n\n\n<script language=\"javascript\" src=\"../../_dwr/interface/NewsvoteDWR.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"../../_dwr/engine.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/news/newscontent.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/ajax.js\"></script><div class=\"team_xq\">\n    <div class=\"team_l  fadeInLeft animated\">\n      <div class=\"team_img\"><img src=\"/__local/D/B2/74/627E65A3AC3901B7CAF13E46913_481D935A_89E43.jpeg\"></div>\n      <p>邮箱：sitongluo@tsinghua.edu.cn</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"team_nr  fadeInRight animated\" data-wow-delay=\".1s\">\n        <div class=\"txt_t\">罗思童 副教授 <i></i></div>\n         \n        <div class=\"txt_xq\">\n          <div class=\"v_news_content\">\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\">罗思童，博士，副教授，特别研究员，博士生导师，主要致力于运用跨学科方法开展健康行为科学及实施科学研究。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">教育经历</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">2014.09 - 2019.03 美国加州大学洛杉矶分校（UCLA），流行病学，博士</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">2011.09 - 2014.01 北京协和医学院（清华大学医学部），流行病与卫生统计学，硕士</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">2007.09 - 2011.07 北京中医药大学，管理学，学士</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">工作经历</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\">2023.12-至今&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\">清华大学万科公共卫生与健康学院，副教授</span></span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\">（2024.6 - 2025.6，清华大学学生社区中心副主任，挂职；2022.4 - 至今，卫健学院第一党支部书记）</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">2021.08 - 2023.11&nbsp; 清华大学万科公共卫生与健康学院，助理教授</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">2019.05 - 2021.05 香港中文大学，健康行为研究中心，博士后</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">2018.06 - 2018.08 人民卫生出版集团，“i卫士”艾滋病人工智能咨询平台，学术顾问（兼职）</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">2015.10 - 2017.09 美国加州大学洛杉矶分校，Semel神经科学与人类行为研究院，科研助理（兼职）</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">2012.07 - 2014.08 中国疾病预防控制中心，性病艾滋病预防控制中心，科研助理（兼职）</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">2012.01 - 2012.03 中国疾病预防控制中心，控烟办公室，科研助理（兼职）</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">研究领域</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\">1. </span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\">传染病防控行为</span><br></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">2. 慢病预防和管理行为</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">3. 卫生组织行为</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">4. 卫生政策实施和评价</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">主持课题（部分）</span></strong></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">1. 国家自然科学基金，面上项目</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">2. 国家自然科学基金，青年项目</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">3. 北京市科技新星计划</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">4. 北京市自然科学基金，海淀联合基金，重点项目</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-wrap: wrap;\">5. 首都卫生发展科研专项，自主创新项目</span><br></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">6. 国家卫健委，促进医防协同医防融合机制研究</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">7. 国家疾控局，疾控领域领军人才能力建设及培养需求研究</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">8. 中国疾病预防控制中心，新冠暴露后预防用药相关科学研究进展分析</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">9. Vital Strategies/中国疾病预防控制中心，控烟广告片脚本信息测试、西宁市无烟法律实施情况评估调查</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">10. 清华大学，科技抗疫重点支持项目、应急支撑项目、</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\">万科基金学科交叉项目、重大支柱项目、启动培育项目</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">【课题组招收博士后和科研助理，欢迎有相似研究兴趣的申请者邮件沟通】</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em; margin-top: 10px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\">教学工作</span></strong></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\">1. Health Behaviors and Health Education（研究生英文专业课，清华大学全球融合式课堂，主讲）</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\">2. 健康行为学：理论、研究及应用（研究生专业课，主讲）</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\">3. 公共卫生研究方法（领军工程博士专业课，参与）</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\">4. 公共卫生与健康（本科生通识课，参与）</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em; margin-top: 10px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\"><strong style=\"text-wrap: wrap;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\">参编教材/专著（部分）</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\">1. 人民卫生出版社，全国高等院校通识课教材《公共卫生与健康》编委</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\">2. 人民卫生出版社，国家卫健委“十四五”规划教材《卫生管理实训》编委兼秘书</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\">3. 人民卫生出版社，全国高等学校预防医学专业第九轮规划教材《卫生事业管理学（第五版）》编委兼秘书</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\">4. 人民卫生出版社，教育部公共卫生与预防医学“101计划”核心教材《健康实施科学》编委</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\">5. 清华大学出版社，《医学检验数据应用与分析》副主编</span></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">学术兼职/社会服务</span></strong></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">1. 世界卫生组织，“行为科学促进健康”技术咨询委员会（Technical Advisory Group on Behavioural Sciences for Better Health)，委员（首位及唯一中国专家）</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">2. 世界卫生组织，驻华代表处，行为科学应用咨询及培训专家</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">3. 国家卫健委，基层卫生健康综合试验区建设专家组成员</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">4.&nbsp;国家卫生健康委，“委领导卫生健康和医改重点联系省份”技术支持专家组成员</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">5. 科技部/国家卫健委/国家疾控局，传染病防控科技发展战略咨询专家</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">6. 中国性病艾滋病防治协会，理事</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">7. 中华预防医学会，社会医学与实施科学分会，委员</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">8. 中国卫生经济学会，基层卫生经济专委会委员</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">9. 中国健康促进与教育协会，健康教育方法学研究分会委员，肥胖防治分会委员，患者行为管理分会委员</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">10. 中国疫苗行业协会，疫苗教育学专委会委员</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">11. 中国人民外交学会，第九届中德青年领导者会议中方代表</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">12. 北京卫生经济学会，卫生技术评估专委会常委</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">13. 北京慢性病防治与健康教育研究会，感染性疾病专委会委员</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">14. 国际行为医学会（ISBM）、国际艾滋病协会（IAS）会员</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">15. Global Transitions, Frontiers in Public Health杂志编委，Lancet Public Health, JMV, JMIR, China CDC Weekly, AIDS and Behavior, Vaccines等杂志审稿人</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\">学术荣誉</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">1. 2021 国际行为医学会（ISBM）“Early Career Award”</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">2. 2019 第三届“一带一路”全球健康论坛青年学者论坛学术报告一等奖</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">3. 2014-2019 美国国立卫生研究院Fogarty艾滋病国际培训及研究项目全额奖学金 </span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">4. 2013 中国性病艾滋病防治协会“艾滋病防治优秀论文”</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">5. 2008 教育部“国家奖学金”</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">论文著作</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">（更新至2024年9月）</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"></span></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">2020-至今</span></strong></p>\n<ul class=\" list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: circle;\">\n <li><p style=\"line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;;\">Huang S, Zhou J, Li Q,…, Luo S*. Media Literacy and Its Potential Influence on Mpox-related Perceptions and Prevention Intentions in China During the 2022 Multi-country Outbreak of Mpox, Health Communication, </span><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;;\">2024 Sep 12:1-11.</span></p></li>\n <li><p style=\"line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;;\">Li Q, Zhang Y, Huang S,…, Luo S*. Depressive symptoms and its multifaceted associated factors among young men who have sex with men facing the dual threats of COVID-19 and mpox in China. J Affect Disord. 2024 Jul 16;363:39-46.</span></p></li>\n <li><p style=\"line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;;\"></span><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;;\">Luo S</span><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;;\">*, Jiao K., Zhang Y et al. Behavioral intention of receiving monkeypox vaccination and undergoing monkeypox testing and the associated factors among young men who have sex with men in China: Large cross-sectional study. JMIR Public Health and Surveillance. 2024 Mar; 10:e47165.</span></p></li>\n <li><p style=\"line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;;\">Xu Y, Jiao K, Zhang Y,…, Luo S*. Behavioral intentions of self-isolation and informing close contacts after developing mpox-related symptoms among young men who have sex with men in China. J Med Virol. </span><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;;\">2024 Feb;96(2):e29470.</span></p></li>\n <li><p style=\"line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;;\">Sun, J., Li, Q., Zhang, Y,…, Ma, F. *, Xiao, L.*, &amp; Luo, S.*. A mix-methods concept testing study of short videos for the national anti-cigarette gift giving campaign in China. Global Transitions, 2024, 6, 1-9.</span></p></li>\n <li><p style=\"line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: &quot;ti